{"tid":793420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首俾中學生做都得","createTime":"2018-08-25T11:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T19:26:33.000Z","uid":177615,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9141d6d201956963455afbb25088123aa8174725","tid":793420,"uid":177615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知填海同拆郊野公園可以增加土地供應<br />\n你求其問個中學生佢地都會諗到<br />\n點解納稅人要俾咁多錢請d同中學生一樣intelligence 既人黎做特首做官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問題在於呢d solution只會破壞生態<br />\n<br />\n政府有冇諗過點解香港出生率咁低都仲係唔夠屋住<br />\n係因為13億中國人個個都想黎香港住呀<br />\n填哂d海拆鳩哂d野都仲係唔會夠土地用<br />\n偏偏政府對呢樣野視若無睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底納稅人人俾錢你地黎服務香港人定大陸人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a83b07bd1d01e2652fc3399974787ea271e1d8","tid":793420,"uid":15078,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7562b6ac5526c55d8641960bafa1556b6b90402f","tid":793420,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"換血係支共大政策黎"},{"pid":"831709def3e9a19ea91cfc5e7d7bfa00af5f4db6","tid":793420,"uid":20816,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"喺街睇緊呢個po㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e8432734a6068e2f91e9051057e511463867d4","tid":793420,"uid":177615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7562b6ac5526c55d8641960bafa1556b6b90402f","tid":793420,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:00:47.000Z","msg":"換血係支共大政策黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:05:11.000Z","msg":"換完d血香港唔再係香港<br />\n優勢蕩然無存<br />\n十年後香港應該連大陸人都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgm